platformAttributes.ios.subtitle.k: Move Your Body, Calm Your Mind

platformAttributes.ios.editorialNotes.ta.k: Your helper for an active life

platformAttributes.ios.editorialNotes.st.k: A more balanced approach to fitness, that rewards little bits of exercise instead of pushing you to your limits. Delightfully designed graphics and rest-day suggestions showcase the kindly encouraging level of care.

Gentler Streaks approach to fitness is carefully crafted for balance. Instead of pushing you to your limits, the app rewards little bits of exercise throughout a day, like dog-walking or daily chores. By suggesting rest days and providing delightfully designed charts and graphics, Gentler Streak showcases a level of care that kindly moves us forward.

Une approche plus quilibre du sport, qui rcompense les petits exercices au lieu de vous pousser dans vos derniers retranchements. Une app qui mise sur la bienveillance, avec de jolis graphismes et des suggestions de jours de repos.
